correctness.rationale: Major factual and schema issues throughout. Schema violations: many fields are set to null/None or wrong types where objects/numbers are required (e.g., processParameters.plasmaPower, supercycleDesign, materialProperties.refractiveIndex/absorptionCoefficient, uniformity.variation, conformality.aspectRatio, filmComposition.elementalConcentration.values.quantityValue.numericValue, deviceProperties.*). Required numeric fields are null (thicknessControl.numberofCycles, flowRates.*.quantityValue.numericValue, nucleationPeriod.numericValue). Dosing/purge time units are incorrect: article reports 1 s DEZn, 5 s H2O, 10 s purge, but extraction uses unit MilliSEC with values 1,5,10 (should be 1000, 5000, 10000 ms). Invented/unsupported values: growthPerCycle 0.2 Å (not in article), bandGap 3.37 eV marked as measured though only a generic value is stated in the intro, crystallinity 'polycrystalline' without evidence, atomicRatio 1:1 not reported, otherAspects filmStability/reproducibility set False without basis, saturation set False without support. Missing/placeholder data: carrierGas and purgingGas are 'Not Found' (not traceable), reactor/deliveryMethod unknown, flow rates absent, nucleationPeriod absent. Multiple processes described in the article (e.g., depositions at 170 °C and 400 °C; special no-purge sample at 200 °C) are not represented as separate processes. Minor: pressure given as a single value (0.3 Torr) though article gives 0.3–0.5 Torr. Correct items include ZnO on sapphire, TALD/ALE, DEZn/H2O, pulse sequence existence, and ~200 nm thickness. To correct: fix dosing/purge units; remove null fields or provide valid values; omit unsupported properties; do not fabricate GPC, band gap, crystallinity, or composition; provide required fields with traceable values only; add separate processes for distinct depositions; ensure all values adhere to schema units and types.

completeness.rationale: Extraction is largely incomplete and contains multiple schema and factual issues. Multiple distinct processes in the article are not represented: at least two ALE/ALD depositions (170 °C and 400 °C) are discussed, plus a modified 200 °C, no‑purge case; only one process is provided. Several required fields are null or placeholders, violating schema and the instruction to avoid nulls: numberofCycles, nucleationPeriod, multiple flow rates, uniformity.variation, conformality.aspectRatio, roughness.value, filmDensity.value, deviceProperties fields, etc. Dosing/purge times are incorrect by units: article reports 1 s (DEZn), 5 s (H2O), and 10 s purge, but extraction encodes 1, 5, 10 MilliSEC instead of 1000, 5000, 10000 ms. ThicknessControl.growthPerCycle (0.2 Å) is not reported in the article; numberofCycles is left null; both violate traceability/unit validity. Pressure is given as a single 0.3 mmHg while the article reports 0.3–0.5 Torr; selected value is not traceable to a specific sample. Several fields are invented or unsupported: bandGap 3.37 eV (general ZnO property, not measured here), filmComposition.atomicRatio 1:1 (not reported), crystallinity set to polycrystalline without evidence. Carrier/purging gases are marked "Not Found" (schema requires concrete values). PlasmaPower is present as null despite thermal ALD (should be omitted, not null). DeviceProperties are included but the article has no TFT devices; filling with nulls contradicts schema and content. Annealing conditions (O2 1 h at 600–1000 °C; N2 RTA 3 min at 700–900 °C) that strongly affect properties are not captured anywhere. To improve, add separate processes for 170 °C and 400 °C depositions (and the 200 °C no‑purge variant if included), correct dose/purge times (convert to ms), remove unreported GPC/atomic ratio/band gap/crystallinity or provide supported values with methods, populate required quantitative fields with valid units or omit optional fields rather than using null/"Not Found", and align pressure and gas details with the article.
